itemDescription: Anglican Dean of Aberdeen and Orkney

wikipedia_page.main: The Very Rev  William Walker , DD, MA was Dean of Aberdeen and Orkney from 1896  to 1906.He was born into a farming family in the Garioch and educated at Aberdeen Grammar School and the city's university. After a curacy at St Andrew,  Aberdeen he was Rector of Monymusk from 1844 to 1900. He died on 11 March 1911.
